msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: component/name
#. +> stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:6
msgid "Kexi"
msgstr "Kexi"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Visual database apps builder"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#. +> trunk5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"KEXI is a visual database applications builder. It can be used for designing "
"database applications, inserting and editing data, performing queries, and "
"processing data. Forms can be created to provide a custom interface to your "
"data. All database objects - tables, queries, forms, reports, etc. - are "
"stored in the database, making it easy to share data and design."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#. +> stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Kexi is a visual database applications builder. It can be used for designing "
"database applications, inserting and editing data, performing queries, and "
"processing data. Forms can be created to provide a custom interface to your "
"data. All database objects - tables, queries, forms, reports, etc. - are "
"stored in the database, making it easy to share data and design."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "機能:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:22
msgid "Full visual designers for tables, queries, forms and reports"
msgstr ""
"テーブル、クエリー、フォームおよびレポートをすべて視覚的にでデザインできます"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:23
msgid "Running queries, support for parametrized queries"
msgstr "クエリーの実行、パラメータ化クエリーのサポート"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:24
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Supports SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL and MS SQL Server databases"
msgid "Direct support for SQLite, MySQL, and PostgreSQL databases"
msgstr ""
"SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL そして MS SQL Server データベースをサポートします"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:19
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Supports SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL and MS SQL Server databases"
msgid ""
"Supports SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL, xBase, and Sybase/MS SQL Server databases"
msgstr ""
"SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL そして MS SQL Server データベースをサポートします"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:25
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The only multiplatform graphical tool importing data from MS Access "
#| "databases"
msgid ""
"The only multiplatform visual tool that can easily import data from MS "
"Access databases"
msgstr ""
"インポートするだけで MS Access データベースにマルチプラットホームのグラフィカ"
"ルツールを提供"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:25
msgid ""
"Scripting using JavaScript, Python or Ruby programming languages "
"(experimental)"
msgstr "JavaScript, Python や Ruby を使用してのスクリプティング(実験的)"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:26
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Supports query design in dedicated SQL view"
msgid "Support for query design in dedicated SQL view"
msgstr "専用の SQL ビューでクエリのデザインをサポート"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:27
msgid ""
"Designing and displaying relational data using combo boxes (lookup columns)"
msgstr "コンボボックスを使用した関係データのデザインと表示(参照列)"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#. +> trunk5 stable5
#: org.kde.kexi.appdata.xml:28
msgid "Direct data entry or import using CSV format"
msgstr "CSV を使用したダイレクトデータの入力もしくはインポート"

